#. module: report_py3o_fusion_server
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/report_py3o_fusion_server/models/ir_actions_report.py:0
#, python-format
msgid ""
"A fusion server or a libreoffice runtime are required to genereate the py3o "
"report '%s'. If the libreofficeruntime is already installed and is not found "
"by Odoo, you can provide the full path to the runtime by setting the key "
"'py3o.conversion_command' into the configuration parameters."
msgstr ""
"Requírese un servidor Fusión ou un tempo de execución de LibreOffice para "
"xerar o informe py3ou '%s'. Se libreofficeruntime xa está instalado e Odoo "
"non o atopa, pode proporcionar o roteiro completo ao tempo de execución "
"configurando a clave 'py3ou.conversion_command' nos parámetros de "
"configuración."

